        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Items</head>
                <p xml:id="del-2020-07-start">
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-13a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T02:37:47.771+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">King Wén opened his storehouses to support the widowed, the orphaned, and those who were alone and without support.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-14a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T02:39:59.804+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">is to take proper care of the people, that is all."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-14a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T02:42:17.671+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">be pleased with them and do not get angry at them,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-14a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T02:44:20.588+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">When the people</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-14a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T02:44:35.715+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">then one is harming them.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-14a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T02:45:46.956+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">then one is ruining them.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-14a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T02:48:03.359+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">then one steals these from the people</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-14a.32" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T02:50:52.06+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">deals with the people like parents loving their children,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-14a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T02:51:13.341+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">like elder</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-15a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T06:27:39.607+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">Rewards one does not</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-15a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T06:30:52.558+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">Anyone who harms the people counts as guilty of a crime,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-15a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T06:33:25.96+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">Anyone who harms the people counts as guilty of a crime;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-15a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T06:33:42.943+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">promoters of worthies and whistleblowers</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-15a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T06:42:04.51+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">below there are no shadowy</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-15a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T16:28:35.488+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">one does not make patterned engravings to please the ear and the eye,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-15a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T16:31:46.247+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">in the public offices there are no</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-16a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T16:45:34.902+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">one is not taking the law as one's standard.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-16a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T16:45:50.352+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">one is not taking the law as one's standard,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-16a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T16:47:04.678+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">one</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-16a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T16:50:34.225+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">Therefore</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-16a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T16:51:58.662+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">"If in running the state one often changes laws and ordinances,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-16a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T16:52:25.187+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">"If in running a state one often revises laws and ordinances</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-16a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T16:52:46.995+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">it is to take what one deems good as one's standard.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-16a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T16:53:06.558+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">Therefore, an ordinance is promulgated and there is unrest.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-16a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T16:53:23.762+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">When there is unrest one revises the laws.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-17a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T20:06:14.38+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-17a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T20:08:39.782+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">In ancient times the ministers of the Xià and the Y</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-17a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T20:14:21.375+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">attacked their own ruler</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-17a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T20:14:49.957+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">attacked their own ruler and rallied to</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-18a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T20:37:14.617+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">I would like the sun and the moon to be in time; (!!!)</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-18a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T20:37:42.419+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">I would</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-18a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T20:39:56.464+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">"A ruler with a thousand charitots</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-18a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T20:40:31.824+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">"Rulers with a thousand chariots</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-18a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T20:46:04.287+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">then the people will not be confused about what to do and what not to do.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-18a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T20:51:03.304+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">"How could this be otherwise?"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-19a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T22:15:03.697+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">"Proper administration consists in</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-19a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T22:19:53.948+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">"Proper administration consists in</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-19a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T22:21:51.419+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">Duke Jǐng of Qí consulted Confucius on administration,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-19a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T22:31:23.032+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">and in foreign politics</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-19a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T22:33:51.854+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">Duke Jǐng of Qí was squandering his money on</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-19a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T22:36:14.938+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">and was extravagant with his parks.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-19a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T22:39:29.398+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">"Proper administration consists in the moderated use of resources.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0938_CHANT_003-13a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#twharbsmeier" modified="2020-07-01T22:42:54.859+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0938-en-fab7ab8b">[Lieber Christian Wittern, hier ist irgendwie der Wurm drinn] rather, it was to enrich the people where they had been poor, make them many where they had been few, make them secure where they had been threatened, and create order where there had been anarchy.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-19a.32" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T23:12:06.307+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">These three cases</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-19a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T23:12:14.602+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">are all administration.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-19a.34" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T23:12:29.467+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">Is it not in the Odes:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-19a.39" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T23:19:24.681+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">but the King</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-19a.37" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T23:20:03.654+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">This person is afflicted by separation, and takes it to be misrule.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-19a.40" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T23:20:43.044+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">This person</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-19a.37" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T23:21:09.512+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">This person is upset by separation, and takes it to be misrule.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-19a.40" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T23:21:20.438+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">This person is upset by wicked ministers keeping the ruler in the dark and takes that to be</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-20a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T23:29:47.472+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">Gōngyí Xiū</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-20a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T23:35:45.029+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">Mount Měng I have not charged taxes from,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-20a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T23:36:38.984+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">cruel orders I have not promulgated:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-20a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-01T23:43:27.553+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">Why should we close the gates?"</seg>
                    <tls:ann xmlns:tls="http://hxwd.org/ns/1.0" concept="SEE" concept-id="uuid-9e93e685-9ba1-4641-8574-5dbec4b244cd" xml:id="uuid-88420966-35ed-424c-8209-6635ed724ca6">
                        <link target="#KR5c0126_tls_005-9a.7 #uuid-2b9fe730-d00d-4d54-8412-577ac4b449cc"/>
                        <tls:text>
                            <tls:srcline title="莊子" target="#KR5c0126_tls_005-9a.7" pos="2">不見已焉爾，
                    </tls:srcline>
                            <tls:line title="莊子 (en)" transl-id="KR5c0126-en-e4e6c215" src="Watson 1969">because they could no longer see their likeness in her;</tls:line>
                        </tls:text>
                        <form corresp="#uuid-9cb6b5ab-c196-4567-b251-048e8cd0f611" orig="">
                            <orth>見</orth>
                            <pron xml:lang="zh-Latn-x-pinyin">jiàn</pron>
                        </form>
                        <sense corresp="#uuid-2b9fe730-d00d-4d54-8412-577ac4b449cc">
                            <gramGrp>
                    <pos>V</pos>
  <tls:syn-func corresp="#uuid-3d128e1e-05ad-4c22-9264-daa895f8f0cd">vt(+N.)postadV</tls:syn-func>
                </gramGrp>
