                    </tls:ann>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-21a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-02T15:58:19.096+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">all these are ugly sides of myself.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-21a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-02T15:58:47.942+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">these are ugly sides of yours, our Master!"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-21a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-02T16:03:13.792+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">Féng Jiǎnzǐ was good at making the political decisions.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-21a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-02T16:06:46.801+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">Gōngsūn Huī understood the doing of the Four States</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-21a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-02T16:09:45.774+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">and he was discriminating in the assessment of the families of the dignitaries.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-21a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-02T16:09:52.927+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">[The text is irredeemably corrupt.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-21a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-02T16:18:58.74+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">When there was</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-21a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-02T16:20:17.37+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">Pí Chén was good at strategic thinking:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-21a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-02T16:20:48.561+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">when he was planning for the countryside he obtained his aims</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-21a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-02T16:21:13.911+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">and</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-22a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-02T16:52:20.355+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">When Dǒng Ānyú governed J</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-22a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-02T16:55:13.795+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">"Where does loyal effort apply?'</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-22a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-02T17:05:15.915+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">"The courage of one's convictions applies to dealing with people who are not good."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-22a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-02T17:06:06.223+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">and there is the courage of one's convictions."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-23a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-02T17:14:00.748+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">Marquis Wén of Wèi sent out Xīmén Bào to run the government in Yè.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-23a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-02T17:15:00.018+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">"You must be completely successful, establish a good name for yourself</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-23a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-02T17:16:22.844+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">May I ask what being</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-23a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-02T17:26:17.783+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">there will be no city without worthy heroes and eloquent men of broad learning,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-23a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-02T17:26:30.511+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">When you go along you must consult the heroic</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-23a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-02T17:29:30.544+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">the elequent and broadly educated</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-23a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-02T17:31:19.676+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">You must not conduct business on special advice from someone.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-23a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-02T17:37:55.781+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">with brightness there is proper order;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-24a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-02T23:08:41.128+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">Mì Zǐjiàn was governing</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-24a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-02T23:09:42.932+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">himself he never descended from his hall</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-24a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-02T23:13:25.193+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">When Wúmǎ Qí governed Shànfù</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-24a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-02T23:21:25.407+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-24a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-02T23:22:58.1+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">of you they say you rely on your strength</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-25a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-05T23:35:51.309+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">He said</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-25a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-05T23:39:58.561+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">and I showed sympathy with the lonely, grieved with the berieved.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-25a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-06T00:31:59.539+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">then one is able to teach fraternal loving respect.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-25a.34" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-06T00:37:15.436+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">"If one is after the big fish</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-25a.36" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-06T00:38:11.661+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">In ancient times Yáo and Shùn were pure and subtle</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-25a.37" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-06T00:38:26.317+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">and they</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-25a.37" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-06T00:38:37.541+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">and they listened to and observed the world</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-25a.36" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-06T00:38:38.34+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">In ancient times Yáo and Shùn were pure and subtle in their persons</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_007-25a.45" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-06T00:41:53.14+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">then I would continue in the footsteps with the Yáos and Shùns of this world.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0009_tls_010-22a.13" xml:lang="en" modified="2020-07-15T01:19:04.006+09:00" resp-del="#wilke" src-id="KR3j0009-en">On the border of Chu an Yue is Deformaty Hill,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0009_tls_010-22a.17" xml:lang="en" modified="2020-07-15T01:19:30.3+09:00" resp-del="#wilke" src-id="KR3j0009-en">and the people of Yue belive in omens,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_005-50a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-07-15T06:20:03.319+09:00" resp-del="#schwermann" src-id="KR2g0003-en-7554120f">                                    was carrying a large parasol</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_005-50a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-07-15T06:25:17.029+09:00" resp-del="#schwermann" src-id="KR2g0003-en-7554120f">Now you are eight chi tall</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2g0003_tls_005-50a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#schwermann" modified="2020-07-15T06:26:30.68+09:00" resp-del="#schwermann" src-id="KR2g0003-en-7554120f">                                    was covered by a large parasol</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2a0001_tls_004-118a.35" xml:lang="en" modified="2020-07-21T20:40:37.967+09:00" resp-del="#wilke" src-id="KR2a0001-en-d4afd8fd">These two women had both hung thenselves.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_007-1a.5" xml:lang="en" modified="2020-07-25T17:56:16.023+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="KR3a0002-en-1fe5781d">in hiss discourse.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1e0877_CHANT_003-72a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-07-26T18:32:44.013+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1e0877-en-7126b138">and the attackee is called kè.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0003_T_007-0252b.95" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2020-07-27T10:26:21.164+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0003-en">Those who would investigate are not infected,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0003_T_007-0252c.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2020-07-27T10:43:43.403+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0003-en">The Venerable Baizhang had a monk come to the master as attendant.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0003_T_007-0252c.96" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2020-07-27T11:05:53.912+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0003-en">On the 12th day of the 12th month in the 13th year of the reign periodYuanhe of the Tang dynasty (818 CE)</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0003_T_007-0253a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2020-07-29T09:44:43.74+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0003-en">‘What does the Great Compassionate One</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0003_T_007-0253a.43" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2020-07-29T10:10:23.7+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0003-en">‘In walking, standing, sitting and lying</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0003_T_007-0253a.46" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2020-07-29T10:13:21.126+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0003-en"> ‘Non-differentiation is Dao.'</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0003_T_007-0253a.47" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2020-07-29T10:13:31.713+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0003-en">The master said,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0003_T_007-0253a.45" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2020-07-29T10:13:41.936+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0003-en">Someone answered,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0003_T_007-0253a.52" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2020-07-29T10:13:50.639+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0003-en"> ‘Non-differentiation is Dao.'</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0003_T_007-0253a.55" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2020-07-29T10:13:53.841+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0003-en"> but still not be capable of acting on the basis of the first principle --</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0003_T_007-0253b.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2020-07-29T12:08:45.933+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0003-en">The National Teacher replie:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR6q0003_T_007-0253b.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2020-07-29T13:13:36.901+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0003-en">xwhere he spoke to the assembly one day, saying,</seg>
                </p>
